  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "SISMA Z4 is a compact, high-output LED wash beam moving head offering an extremely wide zoom range that quickly transforms from a narrow beam of light for dramatic aerial effects to a flood of evenly distributed light with saturated, vibrant colors. Its 60W RGBW Osram LED chips offer industry-leading output while maintaining a lightweight, compact form factor complemented by precise, ultra-fast pan/tilt movements. Its advanced color control can offer, precision-based concentrated colors without compromise to brightness. Sisma is the ultimate dually-capable fixture for dynamic lighting effects that can raise the bar for creative design.",
